msgstr "全局设置，应用于所有 Wi-Fi 无线模块"

msgid "802.11r Mobility Domain"
msgstr "802.11r 移动域"

msgid ""
"4-hex-digit domain identifier shared by all APs that participate in fast "
"roaming (FT). Must be identical on every node. Change this if you have "
"multiple independent mesh networks in the same area to avoid cross-domain FT conflicts."
msgstr ""
"由所有参与快速漫游 (FT) 的 AP 共享的 4 位十六进制域标识符。所有节点必须保持一"
"致。如果你在同一区域拥有多个独立的 Mesh 网络，请修改此值以避免跨域 FT 冲突。"

msgid "802.11r FT Key Mode"
msgstr "802.11r 密钥管理模式"

msgid "Controls how Fast Transition (FT) session keys are shared between APs."
msgstr "控制 AP 之间如何共享快速漫游 (FT) 会话密钥。"

msgid ""
"Distributed FT (advanced) — APs exchange FT keys via RRB protocol. Requires "
"manual r0kh/r1kh peer lists in each AP's wireless config."
msgstr ""
"分布式 FT (高级) — AP 通过 RRB 协议交换 FT 密钥。需要在每个 AP 的无线配置中手"
"动设置 r0kh/r1kh 邻居列表。"

msgid ""
"Local key derivation (recommended) — each AP derives FT keys independently; "
"no inter-AP key sync required. Works correctly out of the box."
msgstr ""
"本地密钥派生 (推荐) — 各 AP 独立生成 FT 密钥；无需 AP 间密钥同步。开箱即用，无"
"需额外配置。"

